      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3, preserved in concours condition. At its heart lies the S54B32 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure VANOS system that delivers linear power up to an 8,000 RPM redline. This specimen features a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and the factory-spec M-Variable differential lock for optimal torque distribution. The chassis remains structurally flawless, with documented subframe reinforcement and a suspension geometry that retains its original rigidity. The exterior retains its factory depth and luster, while the interior shows zero bolster compression or UV degradation. Mechanically synchronized and free of fluid weepage, this M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated Bavarian engineering.",
